folder: Classon Avenue & St. Johns Place, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Classon Avenue - St. Johns Place
text:
Classon Avenue, north from St. Johns Place. On the east side of the avenue are St. Teresa's Auditorium school and church (F. C.)
View 2 shows St. Teresa Church, seen from Park Place.
View 3 is north from near the church.

P.L. Sperr
September 14, 1941
      Views 1-5
